#: ../../source/m5ui/page.rst:4 98899db4da8247289a24df513a722a8e
msgid "M5Page"
msgstr "M5Page"

#: ../../source/m5ui/page.rst:8 383feb9307db418db6254d2b44ec5214
msgid ""
"M5Page is a widget that can be used to create pages in the user "
"interface. It can be used to organize other widgets and provide "
"navigation between different pages."
msgstr "M5Page 是一个可用于在用户界面中创建页面的小部件。它可以用来组织其他小部件，并在不同页面之间提供导航。"

#: ../../source/m5ui/page.rst:12 1c7040b444cb4d0694ffdec3f2469e46
msgid ""
"All m5ui widgets (``M5Label``, ``M5Chart``, ``M5Button``, etc.) must be "
"created with ``parent=page0`` (or another ``M5Page`` instance). If "
"``parent`` is omitted, the widget is attached to the default screen, and "
"calling ``page0.screen_load()`` will load a blank page without those "
"widgets."
msgstr ""

